34:59.030 --> 35:00.832 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
sweet potato farmer.

35:00.932 --> 35:06.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: C.J. is doing well
