36:53.545 --> 36:56.381 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMANDA REISER, Teacher: Make
sure you have
all that copied down.

36:56.481 --> 37:01.619 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Amanda Reiser
teaches sixth
grade in Oxford, Mississippi, a
more affluent

37:01.719 --> 37:04.756 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
