37:43.761 --> 37:45.029 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN TULENKO: Where?

37:45.130 --> 37:47.232 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMANDA REISER: They're hidden
