37:49.000 --> 37:55.306 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Back in Calhoun
County, they're
still using textbooks every day.

37:55.406 --> 38:00.345 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And while computers and Internet
access are
no guarantee of a better
education, without

38:00.445 --> 38:07.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
