SEC will help
you take that situation in your
hand by funding

39:07.845 --> 39:09.647 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
it, that's a game-changer.

39:09.747 --> 39:15.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN TULENKO: Recently, Calhoun
County became
