39:22.126 --> 39:23.962 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mike Moore is superintendent of
schools.

39:24.062 --> 39:26.497 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE MOORE, Superintendent,
Calhoun County
Schools: All of these providers
and all start

39:26.598 --> 39:31.703 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
