here won't have to build their
own network.

39:42.213 --> 39:48.152 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
By inviting outside companies to
bid on the
job or come in with their own
fiber, the district

39:48.253 --> 39:53.591 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
