hopefully not too late for C.J.
Weddle, who

39:59.964 --> 40:01.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
will be a senior.

40:01.866 --> 40:05.303 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
C.J. WEDDLE: I'm a very
